    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >沙漠中一座不可思议的城市</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230560/extras/8197056b6fb8258566ad8ba80e963edb.poster.avif?t=1769550711\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230560/extras/8197056b6fb8258566ad8ba80e963edb.webm?t=1769550711\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230560/extras/8197056b6fb8258566ad8ba80e963edb.mp4?t=1769550711\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《风暴定居者》是一款生存型城市建造游戏，故事背景设定在饱受沙尘暴侵袭的沙漠中。带领你的定居者团队在这片荒凉的环境中建造一座城市。资源匮乏，生存几率低，你唯一的希望就是深入地下，获取地下水，拯救定居点。你会找到水源，还是最终会变成一片荒凉？你的定居点会繁荣昌盛，还是最终被沙尘掩埋？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >抵御风暴</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230560/extras/5ed7bc478ea671cb2d57d70935b629a9.poster.avif?t=1769550711\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230560/extras/5ed7bc478ea671cb2d57d70935b629a9.webm?t=1769550711\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230560/extras/5ed7bc478ea671cb2d57d70935b629a9.mp4?t=1769550711\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沙漠中食物和水源的匮乏并非你面临的唯一挑战。无情的沙尘暴将袭击你的定居点。你必须谨慎选择城市建造地点，并修建城墙，保护你的人民免受沙漠中永不停歇的沙尘侵袭。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特征</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230560/extras/bf5c3aecf9ec638c891828b480678cef.poster.avif?t=1769550711\" width=600 height=148 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230560/extras/bf5c3aecf9ec638c891828b480678cef.webm?t=1769550711\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230560/extras/bf5c3aecf9ec638c891828b480678cef.mp4?t=1769550711\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造一座拥有道路和各种建筑类型的城市，并指派定居者去工作。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎或不欢迎在这片无情的沙漠中寻找定居点的新人们。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >管理你的资源来为你的居民提供食物和水分以维持他们的生存。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >研究技术以获得新建筑和技能来增加您的生存机会。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索沙漠寻找必要的资源。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造围墙并清除蔓延的沙子来抵御沙尘暴。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >研究并建造一个钻头，深入钻探以到达地下水位并拯救殖民地。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过游戏进程解锁化妆品。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有微交易。</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过打碎岩石、种植草和铲沙子来改变地形，以扩大建筑空间。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与旅行商人进行贸易。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深入地、直接地在游戏中，百科全书描述了多种游戏元素的细节。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不同的环境，包括沙漠和苔原生物群落。</p></li></ul>",
